                    <div class="ep-p_text"><a href="https://www.europarl.europa.eu/news/fr/headlines/eu-affairs/20200604STO80505/a-l-agenda-cette-semaine-brexit-classification-covid-19-et-transport-routier" title="Lire la suite"><span class="ep_name">À l’agenda cette semaine: Brexit, classification  Covid-19 et  transport routier</span><span class="ep_icon">&nbsp;</span></a></div>
                </h3>
                <div class="ep_subtitle">
                    <div class="ep-p_text ep-layout_category"><span class="ep_name">Affaires européennes</span><span class="ep_icon">&nbsp;</span></div>
                    
                        
    <div class="ep-p_text ep-layout_date">
        <span class="ep_name">
            
    
    
        <time itemprop="datePublished"
              datetime="2020-06-08T11:38:00">08-06-2020 - 11:38</time>
    

        </span><span class="ep_icon">&nbsp;</span>
    </div>

                    
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="ep-a_text" data-visibility480="false" data-visibility320="false">
                <p>Cette semaine, les députés votent sur les recommandations autour  du Brexit, les  nouvelles règles pour le transport routier et la classification de la Covid-19</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </article>


            

                

    <!-- PRODUCTS -->
    <article class="ep_gridcolumn ep-m_product ep-layout_linkmode " data-view1200="3" data-view1020="3" data-view750="6" data-view640="4" data-view480="8" data-view320="4">
        <div class="ep_gridcolumn-content">
            <div class="ep-a_media" data-visibility480="false" data-visibility320="false">
                <figure>
                    <div class="ep_media ep-layout_image">
                        <div class="ep-p_image ep-layout_thumb ep-layout_media">

                            
    
    <div class="ep_image">
